    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it performs reliably with a smooth engine and transmission, backed by a clear service history. While the exterior still looks great, there are some expected minor stone chips on the hood and a few light scratches consistent with careful use. The interior is clean, comfortable, and well-preserved, making this a dependable choice for its next owner.",
