    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless, with a deep, mirror-like finish and no stone chips, scratches, or imperfections whatsoever. Inside, the cabin remains pristine, with the leather and trim showing zero signs of wear and still retaining that new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously stored and maintained to the highest standards. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in essentially brand-new condition.",
